La Candileja
In Colombia there is a popular story of a character called La candileja,
his real form nobody knows it, since it always presents itself as a ball of
burning fire which nobody can visualize with the naked eye. People say that
torments unfaithful spouses, carefree parents and people who
they attempt against the security of Colombians.
According to legend, there was an extremely consenting grandmother with
his only two grandchildren, who abused such tenderness and abused the
Trust and fragile temperament of his grandmother. All life that lady
He lived to spoil his grandchildren and never allowed them to be educated
correct way. But the day came when the old woman died and when she ascended to purgatory
she found San Pedro and he recriminated her for his lack of education
and a strong hand towards her grandchildren, so I condemn her to wander the land,
wrapped in fire and thus try to pay their penalties.
From there he is found wandering on dark roads, trails and
tormenting drunks. It is said that it appears at dawn, when the
Heaven is illuminated but the sun has not yet come out.
