The dead man of laughter
In the Dominican Republic you can find various popular stories
throughout the region, today we will comment on a not so popular, but
well known in the country's capital and neighborhoods in the vicinity of some
cemeteries. It is said that drunks who roam the city, meet with
a character of high stature, which has an extremely large mouth
and in it, it has teeth with a size of 25 centimeters long. All
people who have seen such a character, claim that after they
Smile, pull out a dagger and give them a great race.
On the other hand, it is said that if the character manages to catch you, you will have to be
your slave for 55 and a half years, and if you try to escape, your whole family
will suffer terrible curses and unimaginable consequences. And even, some
They assure that you can enslave all your family and future generations.
So you know, if you get drunk and try to walk around the city,
It is better that you analyze this idea, since you can find the dead man with laughter.
